about_headline: Protected areas for nature and people
---
about_content: <p>Here you will find data, stories and best practice examples of how natural values can be sustainably used to contribute to the economic and social development within our region.</p>
<p>We hope that these arguments will encourage:<br />
Decision makers in all sectors to account for full range of natural values in developing policies and making sound development decisions.<br />
Business sector to integrate conservation and enhancement of natural and social capital in the business model bottom-lines.<br />
Local communities to take a more active role in the governance of natural resources.<br />
All citizens to take an active role in the effort to safeguard our unique natural values as a basis for our long-term prosperity.</p>
